text: Decent fish soup noodles located at Sunway Big Box. Soup was flavorful and fish was very chunky. Value for money. Iced teh was very aromatic too. Also had a few servings of their sandwiches - peanut butter with cheese and tuna with cheese.
So good to be back at White House Kopi whenever we visit Sunway. Affordable food with quality taste! Not forgetting a free Kaya Toast with every review during your visit

I was amazed by how quickly my food arrived ‚Äì I received it within 10 minutes of placing the order. On top of that, the food tasted amazing! Fresh, flavorful, and definitely worth the wait. Will definitely be ordering again!"

I had a great dining experience here. It was not crowded during my last visit on the weekday morning. The environment is very clean and neat. The food and drinks were served in awhile only. The customer service is great. Highly recommendedüëçüèª
